description: This header file declares external API function prototypes for the Ansc OcoVer1 object in the Cisco RDK Management software, including creation, removal, initialization, and engagement functions.

methods.name: AnscCreateOcoVer1
methods.description: Creates an instance of the OcoVer1 object with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: AnscOcoVer1Create
methods.description: Initializes a new OcoVer1 object with provided context handles.

methods.name: AnscOcoVer1Remove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up an OcoVer1 object.

methods.name: AnscOcoVer1EnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls required objects into the OcoVer1 instance.

methods.name: AnscOcoVer1Engage
methods.description: Engages the OcoVer1 object, starting its operation.

methods.name: AnscOcoVer1Cancel
methods.description: Cancels the operation of the OcoVer1 object.

methods.name: AnscOcoVer1SubEngage
methods.description: Engages sub-components or subordinate functions of the OcoVer1 object.

methods.name: AnscOcoVer1SubCancel
methods.description: Cancels sub-component operations of the OcoVer1 object.
